Comment:
I played a pretty (but probably not very sound) knight sacrifice, getting two pawns and a dangerous pawn roller. Then I won a piece, and the rest was just endgame technique. (not very good technique, because I allowed a pawn fork in time-trouble)


(edit: I'm athorist on the free internet chess server)
